targets.expr:
label_replace(
  histogram_quantile(0.01, rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{
    instance=~"$node",
    shard_id="$shard_id",
    method=~"^Method.*",
  }[$__rate_interval])),
  "display_method",
  "$1",
  "method",
  "^Method\\(([^)]+)\\)"
)
